headline: KFC®'s Big Comeback Continues with More Iconic Throwbacks
summary: After winning hearts with the return of fan-obsessed Wedges and Wings, the fried chicken icon is turning up the flavor once again by answering one of the most requested menu demands of all time: the return of Original Honey BBQ, starting October 6th.
